Yes the previous post was in fact April Fools. Hey Cam lives on! In all seriousness though, even though it was a joke, mental health is very much a real issue. It takes just as much time to comment something nice as it does to comment hate. Cam does get affected by the comments, as we all do. So let’s try to stop with the hate and the bullying. Let’s be better on the internet and think about what we type before we do it. We love all of you and thank you for being such good sports and for supporting us. I hope that we made you laugh and give you some jokes to share with your friends and family! 💙 #heycam
